    <item>
      <title>在德克萨斯州 ICE 设施被拘留数月的家人获释</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/26/us/family-ice-detention-released-dilley-texas.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[获释两天后，这位母亲和她的五个孩子在 ICE 检查期间再次被拘留。法官停止了他们的搬迁，并将他们送回了家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/04/26/us/family-ice-detention-released-dilley-texas.html</guid>
